 redesignated par. (6) as (5) and struck out former par. (5). Prior to amendment, text of par. (5) read as follows: “The term ‘information sharing and analysis organization’ has the meaning given that term in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s671/5"},"text":"section 671(5) of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(6), (7). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/s7143/d/5/A/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, § 7143(d)(5)(A)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", (iii), which redesignated par. (7) as (6) and then directed the general amendment of par. (7), was executed by making the redesignation and generally amending par. (6) as redesignated, to reflect the probable intent of Congress. As amended, such par. remained designated as (7). Prior to amendment, text of par. (7) read as follows: “The term ‘sector risk management agency’ has the meaning given the term ‘Sector-Specific Agency’ in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s651/5"},"text":"section 651(5) of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(3)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/s7143/d/5/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, § 7143(d)(5)(B)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “given such term in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s650"},"text":"section 650 of this title","children":[],"tail":"” for “given such term in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s651/5"},"text":"section 651(5) of this title","children":[],"tail":"”, was executed by making the substitution for “give such term in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s651/5"},"text":"section 651(5) of this title","children":[],"tail":"”, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/s7143/d/5/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, § 7143(d)(5)(C)","children":[],"tail":", made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t6/s665d"},"text":"section 665d of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
